summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 1, 2, 3 and 4, Block 7, White Center Addition, and Lot 2 in an unrecorded subdivision of the east one-half of Tract K, Plat of Alki Point Addition and Second Class Tide Lands adjoining, with respect to Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto one new section numbered 17-123.
